snippet.title: Paperbark - A Story of a Wombat
snippet.description:
Out now on the App Store 
https://itunes.apple.com/au/app/paperbark/id1155399928?mt=8

Now available on Windows + Mac via Steam
https://store.steampowered.com/app/916900/Paperbark/ 

Paperbark is a game that tells a charming short story of the bush, a wombat and a very hot Australian Summer. 

Wander through a beautifully stylised interpretation of Australia, and watch as you bring the illustrated landscape to life.

Story by: Renee Treml
Narrated by: Georgia Maq
Music by: Biddy Conner


For more information:
www.paperbarkgame.com
www.paperhousegames.com
